<span id="Description"></span>
==Opis==

Polecenie '''Przełącz dolne panele''' przełącza widoczność dolnych paneli (zwykle [[Report_View/pl|Widoku raportu]] i [[Python_Console/pl|Konsoli Pythona]]).

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Użycie==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|View →  [[Image:Std_ToggleBottomPanels.svg|16px]] Toggle Bottom Panels}} option from the menu.
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Std_ToggleBottomPanels.svg|16px]] Toggle Bottom Panels}} button in the [[Status_Bar|Status Bar]].
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Ctrl}} + {{KEY|O}}.
</div>


